long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Proofscape Browser Extension enables PDFs from the web to open automatically in PISE, the Proofscape Integrated Study Environment. It also provides a dedicated on-disk PDF cache, to avoid repetitive downloads.
